column5: Did this motel go out of business? Neither of the phone numbers I have work and I can't seem to find any other number. We've stayed there for the past several years on our way up and would like to again this year if I can get ahold of them.
We stay at Telstar Motel in Kakabeka Falls Nice motel phone # 807-473 9211 ask for Jackie $69 per night $75 with tax Larry
How is the parking for trucks and boats? Any problems with things disappearing overnight? We've had real good luck with the Pineview but if I can't get ahold of them I'll have to look elsewhere.
We had a Chevy Suburban and were able to park it with no problem. Why don't you give them a call and ask any questions you may have Larry S
We have reopened year around 807-626-8269 is the new phone number Thank You
